Bic Can Pass On Higher Commodity Prices, CEO Tells Investir

-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 
2011-02-19T11:44:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-19/bic-can-pass-on-higher-commodity-prices-ceo-tells-investir.html
Bic SA is prepared to pass rising
commodities prices on to its customers, raising prices to help
preserve profitability, Chief Executive Officer Mario Guevara
told French magazine  Investir  in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
 fabiobv@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
